my.trt <- ifelse(data$trt=="H",0,1)
jagmodel <- "
model {
for(i in 1:length(hyp)) {
hyp[i] ~ dnorm(mu[i], tau)
mu[i] <- a + b_trt*trt[i]
}
a ~ dnorm(0,1e-04)
b_trt ~ dnorm(0,.01)
tau <- pow(sigma,-2)
sigma ~ dunif(0,15)
}
"
results <- run.jags(jagmodel,monitor=c("a","b_trt","sigma"),method="parallel",data=list(hyp=data$hyp,trt=my.trt))
